title: Francis Dogbatse retains seat as Volta Regional Football Association chairman
text:
13:40 CET Francis Dogbatse retains seat as Volta Regional Football Association chairman - www.ghanasoccernet.com Francis Dogbatse 
Incumbent Francis Dogbatse retained his seat as the Volta Regional Football Association chairman on Monday with a six-vote difference. 
Dogbatse had 37 votes and his challenger Mawutor Agbavitor had 31 of the 68 cast. 
For more Ghana football news visit www.ghanasoccernet.com
